WITH ym_2013 AS (
  SELECT
    ym.CustomerID,
    CAST(substr(ym.Date, 1, 4) AS INTEGER) AS yr,
    ym.Consumption
  FROM yearmonth ym
  WHERE ym.Date BETWEEN '201301' AND '201312'
),
cust_2013 AS (
  SELECT
    c.Segment,
    y.CustomerID,
    SUM(y.Consumption) AS total_2013
  FROM ym_2013 y
  JOIN customers c
    ON c.CustomerID = y.CustomerID
  WHERE y.yr = 2013
    AND c.Currency = 'CZK'
    AND c.Segment IN ('SME','LAM','KAM')
  GROUP BY c.Segment, y.CustomerID
),
min_per_segment AS (
  SELECT
    Segment,
    MIN(total_2013) AS min_total_2013
  FROM cust_2013
  GROUP BY Segment
),
lowest_customers AS (
  SELECT
    c.Segment,
    c.CustomerID,
    c.total_2013
  FROM cust_2013 c
  JOIN min_per_segment m
    ON m.Segment = c.Segment
   AND m.min_total_2013 = c.total_2013
),
avg_lowest AS (
  SELECT
    Segment,
    SUM(total_2013) * 1.0 / COUNT(*) AS annual_avg_consumption_lowest
  FROM lowest_customers
  GROUP BY Segment
),
pivot AS (
  SELECT
    MAX(CASE WHEN Segment = 'SME' THEN annual_avg_consumption_lowest END) AS SME_avg,
    MAX(CASE WHEN Segment = 'LAM' THEN annual_avg_consumption_lowest END) AS LAM_avg,
    MAX(CASE WHEN Segment = 'KAM' THEN annual_avg_consumption_lowest END) AS KAM_avg
  FROM avg_lowest
)
SELECT
  SME_avg - LAM_avg AS diff_SME_minus_LAM,
  LAM_avg - KAM_avg AS diff_LAM_minus_KAM,
  KAM_avg - SME_avg AS diff_KAM_minus_SME
FROM pivot;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing

WITH eur_customers AS (
  SELECT CustomerID
  FROM customers
  WHERE Currency = 'EUR'
),
consumption_by_year AS (
  SELECT
    c.Segment,
    SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4) AS yr,
    SUM(ym.Consumption) AS total_consumption
  FROM yearmonth ym
  JOIN eur_customers ec ON ec.CustomerID = ym.CustomerID
  JOIN customers c ON c.CustomerID = ym.CustomerID
  WHERE SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4) IN ('2012', '2013')
    AND c.Segment IN ('SME', 'LAM', 'KAM')
  GROUP BY c.Segment, SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4)
),
pivot AS (
  SELECT
    Segment,
    SUM(CASE WHEN yr = '2012' THEN total_consumption ELSE 0 END) AS cons_2012,
    SUM(CASE WHEN yr = '2013' THEN total_consumption ELSE 0 END) AS cons_2013
  FROM consumption_by_year
  GROUP BY Segment
)
SELECT
  Segment,
  ROUND(
    CASE
      WHEN cons_2012 = 0 THEN NULL
      ELSE ((cons_2013 - cons_2012) * 100.0) / cons_2012
    END
  , 2) AS pct_increase_2012_to_2013
FROM pivot
ORDER BY CASE Segment
  WHEN 'SME' THEN 1
  WHEN 'LAM' THEN 2
  WHEN 'KAM' THEN 3
  ELSE 4
END;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
